problem counts 10 points. (Depending on degree of
difficulty, some problems will count more points and
this will be marked on the problems.)
*Homeworks must be handed in before 5:10PM on
the due dates. Points will be deducted for late handins.
*For those obviously copied from others, no points
will be given.      

